data.name: button4.ToolTip
data.value: Use this button to reset the weather in case of problems with surge. In this case it's also required to ask for instructions at the OGSE forum.

data.name: disasm.ToolTip
data.value: Disassemble compiled shaders. Enable this only when the developers tell you to do it.

data.name: dsound.Text
data.value: Use DirectSound instead of OpenAL sound

data.name: dsound.ToolTip
data.value: Use an alternative API for sound playing. Enable this option if sound problems are experienced.

data.name: noprefetch.ToolTip
data.value: Disable the game from prefetching some of the textures and models during start. It will help to speed up the game loading, but may result in some lags during the game.

data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value: Here you can tune additional parameters of some graphical effects. Main options are available through the game menu (Options -> Video -> Advanced).
